<del rend="strikethrough">doch </del></ab></add> ob Jr das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_r1l36">alſo 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒetagen</del></ab></add> in freunt</del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_70_line_1576673052305_3361">
<add><ab facs="#facs_70_r1l42">in <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab></add>
